juris-index/
├─ data/                     # raw scraped opinions (JSONL)
├─ index/                    # vector index shards + manifest
├─ scripts/
│  ├─ scrape.py              # pulls opinions (via Juriscraper)
│  ├─ embed.py               # builds embeddings & shards
│  └─ utils.py
├─ .github/workflows/
│  └─ build-index.yml        # runs on a schedule + on demand
├─ requirements.txt
└─ README.md
